@* [CODE(CSS)@@en['max-width']] 特性 (CSS)

[1]
[CITE[HTMLayout CSS support map]] <http://www.terrainformatica.com/htmlayout/cssmap.whtm#foreground-position-attribute>
([[名無しさん]] [sage])

[2]
